trans-unit.source: Interface Attribute is the base interface implemented by any and every printing attribute class to indicate that the class represents a printing attribute.
trans-unit.target: 接口属性(Interface Attribute)是任何一个和每一个打印属性类实现的基础接口,用来表示该类代表一个打印属性。

trans-unit.source: Interface Attribute is the base interface implemented by any and every printing attribute class to indicate that the class represents a printing attribute. All printing attributes are serializable.
trans-unit.target: 接口属性是由任何和每一个打印属性类实现的基础接口,用来表示该类代表一个打印属性。所有的打印属性都是可序列化的。

trans-unit.source: Interface AttributeException is a mixin interface which a subclass of PrintException can implement to report an error condition involving one or more printing attributes that a particular Print Service instance does not support.
trans-unit.target: 接口AttributeException是一个混合接口， PrintException 的子类可以实现该接口以报告涉及特定Print Service实例不支持的一个或多个打印属性的错误情况。

trans-unit.source: Interface AttributeException is a mixin interface which a subclass of PrintException can implement to report an error condition involving one or more printing attributes that a particular Print Service instance does not support. Either the attribute is not supported at all, or the attribute is supported but the particular specified value is not supported. The Print Service API does not define any print exception classes that implement interface AttributeException, that being left to the Print Service implementor's discretion.
trans-unit.target: 接口AttributeException是一个混合接口， PrintException 的子类可以实现该接口以报告涉及特定Print Service实例不支持的一个或多个打印属性的错误情况。根本不支持该属性，或者支持该属性，但是不支持特定的指定值。打印服务API没有定义任何实现接口AttributeException的打印异常类，这些类由打印服务实现者自行决定。

trans-unit.source: Interface AttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of printing attributes.
trans-unit.target: 接口 AttributeSet 指定一组打印属性的接口。

trans-unit.source: Interface AttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of printing attributes. A printing attribute is an object whose class implements interface Attribute.
trans-unit.target: 接口AttributeSet为一组打印属性指定接口。打印属性是一个对象，其类实现接口 Attribute 。

trans-unit.source: Interface Doc affords considerable implementation flexibility. The print data might already be in existence when the doc object is constructed. In this case the objects returned by the doc's methods can be supplied to the doc's constructor, be stored in the doc ahead of time, and simply be returned when called for. Alternatively, the print data might not exist yet when the doc object is constructed. In this case the doc object might provide a "lazy" implementation that generates the print data representation object (and/or the print data) only when the Print Job calls for it (when the Print Job calls the getPrintData() method).
trans-unit.target: Interface Doc提供了相当大的实现灵活性。构造doc对象时，打印数据可能已经存在。在这种情况下，可以将doc方法返回的对象提供给doc的构造函数，提前将其存储在doc中，并在需要时简单地将其返回。或者，在构造doc对象时，打印数据可能还不存在。在这种情况下，doc对象可能会提供“惰性”实现，该实现仅在Print Job调用时（当Print Job调用 getPrintData() 方法时）才生成打印数据表示对象（和/或打印数据）。

trans-unit.source: Interface DocAttribute is a tagging interface which a printing attribute class implements to indicate the attribute denotes a setting for a doc.
trans-unit.target: 接口DocAttribute是一个标记接口,打印属性类实现该接口来表示该属性表示文档的设置。

trans-unit.source: Interface DocAttribute is a tagging interface which a printing attribute class implements to indicate the attribute denotes a setting for a doc. ("Doc" is a short, easy-to-pronounce term that means "a piece of print data.") The client may include a DocAttribute in a Doc's attribute set to specify a characteristic of that doc. If an attribute implements PrintRequestAttribute as well as DocAttribute, the client may include the attribute in a attribute set which specifies a print job to specify a characteristic for all the docs in that job.
trans-unit.target: 接口DocAttribute是一个标记接口，打印属性类实现该接口以指示该属性表示文档的设置。 （“ Doc”是一个简短的，易读的术语，意为“一条打印数据。”）客户端可以在 Doc 的属性集中包括DocAttribute，以指定该doc的特征。如果某个属性 PrintRequestAttribute 实现了PrintRequestAttribute又实现了DocAttribute，则客户端可以将该属性包括在属性集中，该属性集中指定打印作业以为该作业中的所有文档指定特征。

trans-unit.source: Interface DocAttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of doc attributes, i.e. printing attributes that implement interface DocAttribute. In the Print Service API, the client uses a DocAttributeSet to specify the characteristics of an individual doc and the print job settings to be applied to an individual doc.
trans-unit.target: 接口DocAttributeSet为一组doc属性指定接口，即打印实现接口 DocAttribute 的属性。在打印服务API中，客户端使用DocAttributeSet来指定单个文档的特征以及要应用于单个文档的打印作业设置。

trans-unit.source: Interface FlavorException is a mixin interface which a subclass of PrintException can implement to report an error condition involving a doc flavor or flavors (class DocFlavor).
trans-unit.target: 接口FlavorException是一个混合接口， PrintException 的子类可以实现该接口以报告涉及一个或多个doc风格的错误情况（ DocFlavor 类）。

trans-unit.source: Interface FlavorException is a mixin interface which a subclass of PrintException can implement to report an error condition involving a doc flavor or flavors (class DocFlavor). The Print Service API does not define any print exception classes that implement interface FlavorException, that being left to the Print Service implementor's discretion.
trans-unit.target: 接口FlavorException是一个混合接口， PrintException 的子类可以实现该接口以报告涉及一个或多个doc风格的错误情况（ DocFlavor 类）。打印服务API没有定义任何实现接口FlavorException的打印异常类，这些类由打印服务实现者自行决定。

trans-unit.source: Interface MultiDoc provides an abstraction similar to a "linked list" of docs. A multidoc object is like a node in the linked list, containing the current doc in the list and a pointer to the next node (multidoc) in the list. The Print Job can call the multidoc's getDoc() method to get the current doc. When it's ready to go on to the next doc, the Print Job can call the multidoc's next() method to get the next multidoc, which contains the next doc. trans-unit.source: Interface MultiDoc specifies the interface for an object that supplies more than one piece of print data for a Print Job.
trans-unit.target: 接口 MultiDoc 指定了为打印作业提供多个打印数据的对象的接口。

trans-unit.source: Interface MultiDoc specifies the interface for an object that supplies more than one piece of print data for a Print Job. "Doc" is a short, easy-to-pronounce term that means "a piece of print data," and a "multidoc" is a group of several docs. The client passes to the Print Job an object that implements interface MultiDoc, and the Print Job calls methods on that object to obtain the print data.
trans-unit.target: 接口MultiDoc指定了一个对象的接口,该对象为一个打印作业提供了多个打印数据。"Doc "是一个简短、易读的术语,意思是 "一块打印数据",而 "multidoc "是由多个Doc组成的一组。客户端向打印任务传递一个实现接口MultiDoc的对象,打印任务调用该对象上的方法来获取打印数据。

trans-unit.source: Interface MultiPrintService is the factory for a MultiDocPrintJob.
Interface MultiPrintService is the factory for a MultiDocPrintJob. A MultiPrintService describes the capabilities of a Printer and can be queried regarding a printer's supported attributes.
trans-unit.target: 接口MultiPrintService是MultiDocPrintJob的工厂。MultiPrintService描述了打印机的功能,可以查询打印机支持的属性。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintJobAttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of print job attributes, i.e. printing attributes that implement interface PrintJobAttribute. In the Print Service API, a service uses a PrintJobAttributeSet to report the status of a print job.
trans-unit.target: 接口PrintJobAttributeSet为一组打印作业属性（即实现接口 PrintJobAttribute 的打印属性）指定接口。在打印服务API中，服务使用PrintJobAttributeSet来报告打印作业的状态。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintRequestAttribute is a tagging interface which a printing attribute class implements to indicate the attribute denotes a requested setting for a print job.
trans-unit.target: 接口PrintRequestAttribute是一个标记接口,打印属性类实现该接口,表示该属性表示打印作业的请求设置。

trans-unit.target: 接口 PrintRequestAttributeSet 指定了打印请求属性集的接口,即打印请求属性。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintRequestAttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of print request attributes, i.e. printing attributes that implement interface PrintRequestAttribute. The client uses a PrintRequestAttributeSet to specify the settings to be applied to a whole print job and to all the docs in the print job.
trans-unit.target: 接口PrintRequestAttributeSet为一组打印请求属性（即实现接口 PrintRequestAttribute 的打印属性）指定接口。客户端使用PrintRequestAttributeSet来指定要应用于整个打印作业以及该打印作业中所有文档的设置。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintService is the factory for a DocPrintJob.
Interface PrintService is the factory for a DocPrintJob. A PrintService describes the capabilities of a Printer and can be queried regarding a printer's supported attributes.
trans-unit.target: 接口 PrintService 是 DocPrintJob 的工厂。PrintService描述了打印机的功能,并且可以查询打印机的支持属性。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintServiceAttribute is a tagging interface which a printing attribute class implements to indicate the attribute describes the status of a Print Service or some other characteristic of a Print Service.
trans-unit.target: 接口PrintServiceAttribute是一个打印属性类实现的标记接口,它表示该属性描述了打印服务的状态或打印服务的其他一些特性。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintServiceAttribute is a tagging interface which a printing attribute class implements to indicate the attribute describes the status of a Print Service or some other characteristic of a Print Service. A Print Service instance adds a number of PrintServiceAttributes to a Print service's attribute set to report the Print Service's status.
trans-unit.target: 接口PrintServiceAttribute是一个标记接口,打印属性类实现该接口,以表示该属性描述了一个打印服务的状态或打印服务的一些其他特性。一个打印服务实例将一些PrintServiceAttributes添加到打印服务的属性集,以报告打印服务的状态。

trans-unit.source: Interface PrintServiceAttributeSet specifies the interface for a set of print job attributes, i.e. printing attributes that implement interface PrintServiceAttribute. In the Print Service API, the Print Service instance uses a PrintServiceAttributeSet to report the status of the print service.
